The Telegraph - Calcutta : International
 Wednesday, April 28, 2004 				 Halle Berry files for divorce
																								Los Angeles, April 27 (Reuters): Oscar-winning actress Halle Berry has filed for divorce from her second husband, R amp;B singer Eric Benet, six months after the couple separated, her attorney said today.																								In a divorce petition filed yesterday in Los Angeles, Berry cited irreconcilable differences as the reason for the split, attorney Neal Hersh said. 																								In a statement issued last October when the couple announced their separation, Berry said: Eric and I have had marital problems for some time. 
